@RefuelAPI_HostAddress = http://localhost:5094

###Create

POST {{RefuelAPI_HostAddress}}/api/v1/Vehicles/
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "Brand": "Alfa Romeo",
  "Model": "Giulia",
