}


### Get All
GET {{RefuelAPI_HostAddress}}/api/v1/Vehicles
Accept: application/json


### Get by id 

GET {{RefuelAPI_HostAddress}}/api/v1/Vehicles/157ac01f-a604-4549-8972-bb3f6a09fd62
Accept: application/json



### Get refuels 

GET {{RefuelAPI_HostAddress}}/api/v1/Vehicles/9877dee6-a583-45d5-bbd5-1653410f633a/refuels
Accept: application/json


